page_0: "Recovering the golden medallion of Saint Burringden will reward all the sweat I put into the endless hunt for those damned talismans.  By selling it I will surely make some profit off of this ordeal. In all my years of service to the Hand I have never seen their efforts so thoroughly stymied. It’s almost as though one of their own had taken and hidden the talismans so completely that not even the archmages can find them. 

- Capt. E. F. Regalio"